{
  "texts": [
    "Expert generator training We trained five expert generators, each dedicated to generating text corresponding to one of the Big Five personality traits.",
    "More training details about the expert generator are explained in Appendix D.4.",
    "We implemented two baseline prompting strategies to induce personality traits in LLMs.",
    "The first strategy, instruction-based prompting, directly instructs the model to exhibit specific Big Five traits.",
    "The second strategy, demonstration-based prompting, involves providing the model with 10 in-context examples randomly selected from our BIG5-CHAT dataset to demonstrate the behaviors corresponding to the desired traits."
  ]
}